<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Aura Coffee</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Segoe UI;
}

body{
background-color:#1b100a;
color:white;
}

/* NAVBAR */

nav{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:20px 80px;
background:#120907;
}

nav h2{
color:#d4a373;
letter-spacing:2px;
}

nav ul{
display:flex;
list-style:none;
}

nav ul li{
margin-left:25px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:0.3s;
}

nav ul li:hover{
color:#d4a373;
}

/* HERO */

.hero{
height:90vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;

background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6),rgba(0,0,0,0.6)),
url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:60px;
letter-spacing:3px;
}

.hero p{
margin-top:15px;
font-size:18px;
color:#e5e5e5;
}

.hero button{
margin-top:25px;
padding:14px 35px;
border:none;
background:#d4a373;
color:black;
font-size:16px;
border-radius:6px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:0.3s;
}

.hero button:hover{
transform:scale(1.08);
}

/* MENU */

.menu{
padding:80px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.menu h2{
margin-bottom:40px;
color:#d4a373;
}

.menu-items{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:25px;
}

.item{
background:#2b1a14;
width:230px;
border-radius:10px;
overflow:hidden;
transition:0.3s;
}

.item:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.item img{
width:100%;
height:150px;
object-fit:cover;
}

.item-content{
padding:20px;
}

.item h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* ABOUT */

.about{
padding:80px 20px;
text-align:center;
max-width:800px;
margin:auto;
}

.about h2{
color:#d4a373;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.about p{
line-height:1.7;
color:#ddd;
}

/* CONTACT */

.contact{
text-align:center;
padding:60px;
background:#120907;
}

.contact h2{
color:#d4a373;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

/* FOOTER */

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
background:#0b0503;
color:#aaa;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<nav>

<h2>Aura Coffee</h2>

<ul>
<li>Home</li>
<li>Menu</li>
<li>About</li>
<li>Contact</li>
</ul>

</nav>


<section class="hero">

<h1>Aura Coffee</h1>

<p>Fresh Coffee. Cozy Vibes.</p>

<button>Order Now</button>

</section>


<section class="menu">

<h2>Our Menu</h2>

<div class="menu-items">

<div class="item">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1510707577719-ae7c14805e3a">
<div class="item-content">
<h3>Espresso</h3>
<p>Rich and bold coffee shot.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="item">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461023058943-07fcbe16d735">
<div class="item-content">
<h3>Cappuccino</h3>
<p>Perfect blend of coffee and milk foam.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div <div class="item">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1561882468-9110e03e0f78">
<div class="item-content">
<h3>Latte</h3>
<p>Smooth coffee with creamy milk.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="item">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517701604599-bb29b565090c">
<div class="item-content">
<h3>Mocha</h3>
<p>Chocolate flavored coffee delight.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</section>


<section class="about">

<h2>About Aura Coffee</h2>

<p>
At Aura Coffee we believe coffee is more than a drink — it's an experience.
Our cafe offers freshly brewed coffee, cozy atmosphere, and the perfect
place to relax, work, or meet friends.
</p>

</section>


<section class="contact">

<h2>Visit Us</h2>

<p>📍 IT Park, Nagpur</p>
<p>📞 8208348127</p>
<p>✉ contact@auracoffee.com</p>

</section>


<footer>

<p>© 2026 Aura Coffee</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
